-Sure.

807
01:21:35,600 --> 01:21:37,300
Go see this nice lady.

808
01:21:38,000 --> 01:21:40,500
l just wanna talk to him
for a minute.

809
01:21:44,100 --> 01:21:47,100
-What are you doing?
-What am l supposed to do?

810
01:21:47,300 --> 01:21:51,900
