l couldn't call you direct.

843
01:25:53,700 --> 01:25:55,800
What's going on?

844
01:25:56,500 --> 01:25:58,700
l have something you should see.

845
01:25:59,000 --> 01:26:02,600
Could we meet at York
and 59th Street Bridge?

